title: New: Eves the Behavior – Electrical
content:
Brisbane’s Eves the Behavior has seriously got the hang of absolutely nailing huge choruses.

Her ‘debut’ single of sorts, TV, proved one of this years most addictive offerings, and her newest cut, Electrical, follows a similar path. Not a million miles from several of the tracks from Sky Ferreira’s 2013 debut album, it’s another promising step forward for Hannah Karydas.

Follow our Spotify On Repeat playlist for a selection of the current hottest tracks.
